{"tid":2110103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：即使曼城跌落英乙 我都會留效","createTime":"2020-07-15T15:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T08:38:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08936fe745e99171ca147248c1421339b705c00c","tid":2110103,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"早前曼城面臨兩年歐洲賽禁賽令，令人擔心一旦上訴失敗，領隊哥迪奧拿和包括迪布尼在內的球星會離隊。如今曼城上訴成功，即有人討論關於哥帥會否延長其到2021年6月屆滿的合約。<br />\n<br />\n曼城接下來除了聯賽餘下賽事，還有足總盃4強對阿仙奴和歐聯硬碰皇馬的大戰。說到續約，哥帥坦言：「現在不是講合約的適當時機，接下來我們有精彩的1個月。我的合約尚有1年，對於領隊來說，這是很長很長的時間。我個人而言很清晰，1個月前我說過會留隊，不論我們在歐聯，還是如這裡的人說踢英乙，我也會留下。將來，我們有精彩的4、5個星期等待著我們，要對戰阿仙奴和皇馬。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3yL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=61756a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"a6bc83c21682ba0c4afc92ff98584974435564de","tid":2110103,"uid":62891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"假撚到"},{"pid":"0a3b6b6f4f2606dc5dbc4cdf22607c2f78332bc8","tid":2110103,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"上訴成功咪咁講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身佢google緊都靈住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3a92d140c08971d9025370e1c80da968d4ac57","tid":2110103,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6bc83c21682ba0c4afc92ff98584974435564de","tid":2110103,"uid":62891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"假撚到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"我識佢真人，佢早排仲問我都靈邊度有鴨叫"},{"pid":"410216ff3e991627d99cfd39f6ee3bf7caf65c02","tid":2110103,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f3a92d140c08971d9025370e1c80da968d4ac57","tid":2110103,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6bc83c21682ba0c4afc92ff98584974435564de","tid"